These are the different commands for running each type of method:

MPI4PY
- mpirun -np 3 python -m cProfile LebwohlLasher_MPI_4PY 50 50 1 0 > LL-3-50-50-1-0-6

Cython
- Setup python "".py build_ext -fi
- Run  python -m cProfile "Run_file".py 50 50 1 0 > LL-3-50-50-1-0-6

Cython OpenMP - Same as Cython; however, you have to mention the number of threads.
- OMP_NUM_THREADS=8 python -m cProfile LebwohlLasher_MPI_4PY 50 50 1 0 > LL-3-50-50-1-0-6


Normal scripts for Numba and Python General
- does not require setup files you just run it 
- python -m cProfile LebwohlLasher_MPI_4PY 50 50 1 0 > LL-3-50-50-1-0-6
